{"tid":2386140,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"學資處借錢可唔可以由拎支票改返做入個戶口?","createTime":"2021-01-29T11:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T07:15:34.000Z","uid":370862,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"61dfcefd2c746f714ec41018af78f27ea7d42933","tid":2386140,"uid":370862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T11:36:56.000Z","msg":"話說借左政府錢讀緊master<br />\n第一個sem因為自己交左先所以第一個sem d錢入個人戶口<br />\n第二個sem suppose係要去學資處拎返張支票直接比大學<br />\n但係依個星期學資處有人染左武漢肺炎，琴日開返又撞正我要返工<br />\n下星期全星期都返工根本拎唔到支票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但已經deadline<br />\n其實可唔可以自己交住先，之後叫學資處取消返張支票改做入我戶口?<br />\n<br />\n因為就算去大學申請遲交學費，又要自己交張表去大學<br />\n我如果有依d時間一早都拎左支票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e849a1a04f2216360ac8e46149e5a0db1f3c1f","tid":2386140,"uid":143878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:38:20.000Z","msg":"打去問啦直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfd21aea9a60bd163251ac7844640221e83a9e6","tid":2386140,"uid":370862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"29e849a1a04f2216360ac8e46149e5a0db1f3c1f","tid":2386140,"uid":143878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T02:38:20.000Z","msg":"打去問啦直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T07:15:34.000Z","msg":"琴日星期五，今日星期六，聽日又星期日<br />\n如果打到都打左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}